Heat oven to 400 degrees F. Spread tops of each pita with approximately 2 tablespoons tomato paste; sprinkle each with 1 1/2 tablespoons Parmesan cheese. Top each in the following order: 1/4 cup chicken, 2 tablespoons mushrooms, 2 tablespoons olives and 1/3 cup mozzarella cheese. Bake 10 to 12 minutes or until cheese is melted.